    <title>Markdown的常用写法</title>
    <link href="https://zhouhengheng.com/Markdown%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95.html"/>
    <id>https://zhouhengheng.com/Markdown的写法.html</id>
    <published>2018-11-21T13:08:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-12-31T04:47:32.236Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<font size="4"><strong>hexo博客的文章都是用Markdown格式编写的，所以要想熟练的编写hexo博客的话，一些常用的格式还是需要了解一下的，本篇介绍几个常用的Markdown写法，有兴趣的小伙伴们可以学习一下。</strong></font><p><img src="https://github.com/zhouhengheng0705/zhouhengheng0705.github.io/blob/master/Markdown%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95/super_mario_history-wallpaper-960x600.jpg?raw=true" alt="&quot;Markdown&quot;"><br><a id="more"></a></p><font size="4"><strong>1.列表</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line"> - The Beatles</span><br><span class="line">  - Atom</span><br><span class="line">    - git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">※注意:「-」和文字之间有半角空格。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>2.标题</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line"># 标题1</span><br><span class="line">## 标题2</span><br><span class="line">### 标题3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">※注意:「#」和文字之间有半角空格。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>3.强调</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line">**Hello World**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>4.引用</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line">&gt; Beautiful is better than ugly.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">※注意:「&gt;」和文字之间有半角空格。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>5.链接</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line">[我的博客](http://www.zhouhengheng.com)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>6.取消线</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line">~~取消~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>7.水平线</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">格式: 从「&gt;」，「_」，「*」中任意并列三个以上</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">___</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>8.插入图片</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">格式: ![代替文字](图片URL “标题”)」）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![名片工厂图片](https://meishi.artisj.com/summary/image/logo.gif &quot;名片工厂&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>9.段落和改行</strong></font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">段落空一整行。</span><br><span class="line">改行空两个半角空格以上。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">你学会使用Markdown格式了吗？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">只会一点，</span><br><span class="line">还在学习中。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="4"><strong>10.段首空格/段首缩进</strong></font><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">格式:</span><br><span class="line">&amp;nbsp;//半角空格</span><br><span class="line">&amp;emsp;//全角空格</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&amp;emsp;我叫张三。&amp;nbsp;我喜欢学习和分享。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><br><font size="4"><strong>11.代码引用</strong></font><p>①指定开发语言时</p><p>例:</p><p>```python</p><p>def hello_world():<br>    print(‘Hello world!’)</p><p>hello_world()</p><p>```</p><p>②未指定开发语言时</p><p>例:</p><p>```</p><p>print(‘Hello world!)</p><p>```</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;hexo博客的文章都是用Markdown格式编写的，所以要想熟练的编写hexo博客的话，一些常用的格式还是需要了解一下的，本篇介绍几个常用的Markdown写法，有兴趣的小伙伴们可以学习一下。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://github.com/zhouhengheng0705/zhouhengheng0705.github.io/blob/master/Markdown%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95/super_mario_history-wallpaper-960x600.jpg?raw=true&quot; alt=&quot;&amp;quot;Markdown&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
